## Proposed Architecture — Two-Phase Pipeline

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The core optimization is: **extract once, analyze twice**. Calls 3 (SM) and 4 (EA) should work from the **structured JSON output of Call 2**, not from the raw PDF. This eliminates 2 full PDF re-reads (~116K tokens saved, ~50% reduction).

```mermaid
